replenishing the substrate for NO production with L-Arg. This is the first study to demonstrate that NO plays an important role in the anti-fibrillatory effect of VNS on the rabbit ventricle, possibly via effects on APD restitution.},
   author = {Kieran E Brack and Vanlata H Patel and John H Coote and G André Ng},
   doi = {10.1113/jphysiol.2007.138461},
   isbn = {0022-3751 (Print)\r0022-3751 (Linking)},
